content.original: Argo, we've taken control of the facility. You need to keep it intact and neutralize the attackers.
content.prevOriginal: Argo, we've taken control of the facility. You need to keep it intact and neutralize the attackers.
content.content: 阿尔戈，我们已经控制了设施。你需要保持它完好无损并中和攻击者。

content.original: Acknowledged. Meyer, what's it looks like from up there?
content.prevOriginal: Acknowledged. Meyer, what's it looks like from up there?
content.content: 承认。迈耶，从上面看是什么样子？

content.original: Uh, have you ever seen an angry ant colony? There's a few Companies of light tanks out there.
content.prevOriginal: Uh, have you ever seen an angry ant colony? There's a few Companies of light tanks out there.
content.content: 呃，你见过愤怒的蚁群吗？外面有几个连的轻型坦克。

content.original: Commander, they're going to be gunning for this this base. You'll need to get their attention.
content.prevOriginal: Commander, they're going to be gunning for this this base. You'll need to get their attention.
content.content: 指挥官，他们要瞄准这个基地。你得引起他们的注意。

content.original: The good news is that once you take out the base they captured they'll have nothing more to fight for here, so they'll probably stop landing more forces.
content.prevOriginal: The good news is that once you take out the base they captured they'll have nothing more to fight for here, so they'll probably stop landing more forces.
content.content: 好消息是，一旦你摧毁了他们占领的基地，他们将没有更多的战斗在这里，所以他们可能会停止登陆更多的部队。

content.original: Commander, I'll move in for a pickup once you get that base flattened. Don't keep me waiting.
content.prevOriginal: Commander, I'll move in for a pickup once you get that base flattened. Don't keep me waiting.
content.content: 指挥官，一旦你把基地夷为平地，我就去找辆皮卡。别让我久等了。

content.original: We've got it from here, Argo. Thanks for the help.
content.prevOriginal: We've got it from here, Argo. Thanks for the help.
content.content: 我们从这里拿到了，阿尔戈。谢谢你的帮助。

content.original: Another job well done.
content.prevOriginal: Another job well done.
content.content: 另一项工作做得很好。

content.original: That could have gone better. Let's debrief back in orbit, Commander.
content.prevOriginal: That could have gone better. Let's debrief back in orbit, Commander.
content.content: 本来可以做得更好的。我们回轨道汇报吧，指挥官。

content.original: Commander, enemy turrets identified.
content.prevOriginal: Commander, enemy turrets identified.
content.content: 指挥官，发现敌人炮塔。

content.original: I'm seeing another lance of Scorpions hanging back near the enemy base.
content.prevOriginal: I'm seeing another lance of Scorpions hanging back near the enemy base.
content.content: 我看到另一支蝎子长矛挂在敌人基地附近。

content.original: We can't complete the contract until those units are destroyed.
content.prevOriginal: We can't complete the contract until those units are destroyed.
content.content: 在那些单位被摧毁之前，我们不能完成合同。

content.original: Guess what boss, more Scorpions.
content.prevOriginal: Guess what boss, more Scorpions.
content.content: 你猜什么老板，更多的蝎子。

content.original: That's the first target structure down, Commander. Keep up the pressure.
content.prevOriginal: That's the first target structure down, Commander. Keep up the pressure.
content.content: 那是第一个目标建筑，指挥官。保持压力。

content.original: Argo, our facility is taking fire over here. We need you to draw that fire off, or we're dead!
content.prevOriginal: Argo, our facility is taking fire over here. We need you to draw that fire off, or we're dead!
content.content: 阿尔戈，我们的设施在这里着火了。我们需要你把火引开，否则我们就死定了！

content.original: Argo, we've lost one of our structures. You've got to move faster, or we'll lose them all!
content.prevOriginal: Argo, we've lost one of our structures. You've got to move faster, or we'll lose them all!
content.content: 阿尔戈，我们失去了一个建筑。你得快点，否则我们会失去他们的！

content.original: Argo, we're under heavy-- [static]-- hold out-- [static]
content.prevOriginal: Argo, we're under heavy-- [static]-- hold out-- [static]
content.content: 阿尔戈，我们在沉重的--[静态]--坚持住--[静态]

content.original: Dammit! Commander, we've only got one building left. If it goes down, I'm scrubbing the contract.
content.prevOriginal: Dammit! Commander, we've only got one building left. If it goes down, I'm scrubbing the contract.
content.content: 该死！指挥官，我们只剩下一栋楼了。如果失败了，我就取消合同。

content.original: That's the last structure, Commander. That should slow down the attackers. Meyer, are you ready for pickup?
content.prevOriginal: That's the last structure, Commander. That should slow down the attackers. Meyer, are you ready for pickup?
content.content: 那是最后一个结构，指挥官。那应该会减慢袭击者的速度。迈耶，准备好接人了吗？

content.original: Affirmative, XO. Let's get out of here, boss.
content.prevOriginal: Affirmative, XO. Let's get out of here, boss.
content.content: 肯定，XO。我们离开这里，老大。

content.original: Commander, we've completed all the primary objectives and you're clear to extract.
content.prevOriginal: Commander, we've completed all the primary objectives and you're clear to extract.
content.content: 指挥官，我们已经完成了所有主要目标，你可以撤离了。

content.original: I'm on station to pick you up here whenever you're ready, boss.
content.prevOriginal: I'm on station to pick you up here whenever you're ready, boss.
content.content: 你准备好了我就在车站接你，老大。

content.original: As long as you're still in the AO, Commander, you'll need to keep the {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} base secure.
content.prevOriginal: As long as you're still in the AO, Commander, you'll need to keep the {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} base secure.
content.content: 只要你还在AO里，指挥官，你就需要保护{team_emp.factiondef.demonym}基地的安全。

content.original: Commander, that's all the enemy forces. There's a {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} lance ready to relieve you.
content.prevOriginal: Commander, that's all the enemy forces. There's a {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} lance ready to relieve you.
content.content: 指挥官，敌军就这些。有一支{team_emp.factiondef.demonym}长矛准备解除你的职务。

content.original: When you're ready to extract, Sumire will pick you up at this location.
content.prevOriginal: When you're ready to extract, Sumire will pick you up at this location.
content.content: 当你准备好提取时，Sumire会在这个位置接你。

content.original: Heads up, commander, a lance of {TEAM_HOST.FactionDef.Demonym} units just entered the area. They're hostile to everyone!
content.prevOriginal: Heads up, commander, a lance of {TEAM_HOST.FactionDef.Demonym} units just entered the area. They're hostile to everyone!
content.content: 注意，指挥官，一支由{team_host.factiondef.demonym}组成的长矛刚刚进入该地区。他们对每个人都怀有敌意！

content.original: We'll have to destroy that lance if we want to complete the mission.
content.prevOriginal: We'll have to destroy that lance if we want to complete the mission.
content.content: 如果我们想完成任务，就得毁掉那支长矛。

content.original: Heads up, commander, a lance of {TEAM_HOST.FactionDef.Demonym} units just entered the area. They're hostile to everyone!
content.prevOriginal: Heads up, commander, a lance of {TEAM_HOST.FactionDef.Demonym} units just entered the area. They're hostile to everyone!
content.content: 注意，指挥官，一支由{team_host.factiondef.demonym}组成的长矛刚刚进入该地区。他们对每个人都怀有敌意！

content.original: If we destroy them we'll get a hefty bonus.
content.prevOriginal: If we destroy them we'll get a hefty bonus.
content.content: 如果我们摧毁它们，我们会得到一大笔奖金。

content.original: Commander, I'm seeing hostile {TEAM_TAR_ALLY.FactionDef.Demonym} units in the area. Our target brought in allies for backup.
content.prevOriginal: Commander, I'm seeing hostile {TEAM_TAR_ALLY.FactionDef.Demonym} units in the area. Our target brought in allies for backup.
content.content: 指挥官，我在该地区看到敌对的{team_tar_ally.factiondef.demonym}单位。我们的目标带来了盟军支援。

content.original: Our employer is saying we NEED to kill those units. Prepare to engage.
content.prevOriginal: Our employer is saying we NEED to kill those units. Prepare to engage.
content.content: 我们的雇主说我们需要干掉那些单位。准备交战。

content.original: Commander, I'm seeing hostile {TEAM_TAR_ALLY.FactionDef.Demonym} units in the area. Our target brought in allies for backup.
content.prevOriginal: Commander, I'm seeing hostile {TEAM_TAR_ALLY.FactionDef.Demonym} units in the area. Our target brought in allies for backup.
content.content: 指挥官，我在该地区看到敌对的{team_tar_ally.factiondef.demonym}单位。我们的目标带来了盟军支援。

content.original: If we decide to kill these units our employer if offering a bonus.
content.prevOriginal: If we decide to kill these units our employer if offering a bonus.

content.prevOriginal: I hope that was enough data for the {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} scientists.

content.original: Commander, I'm not sure what went wrong, but we'll need to prepare some explanations for our employers.
content.prevOriginal: Commander, I'm not sure what went wrong, but we'll need to prepare some explanations for our employers.
content.content: 指挥官，我不确定哪里出了问题，但我们需要为我们的雇主准备一些解释。

content.prevOriginal: New contacts on sensors, Commander. These units don't match {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.ShortName} signatures. We've got a new player on the field.

content.original: Kilo 1-3 just got smoked! Suffering loses over here, Commander! We're still in the fight, but down one.
content.prevOriginal: Kilo 1-3 just got smoked! Suffering loses over here, Commander! We're still in the fight, but down one.
content.content: 1-3公斤刚刚被熏了！在这里受苦受难，指挥官！我们还在战斗，但下降了一个。

content.prevOriginal: Grace under fire, folks. Lay it on 'em!

content.original: We lost Quebec Two Commander.
content.prevOriginal: We lost Quebec Two Commander.
content.content: 我们失去了魁北克的两个指挥官。

content.prevOriginal: This is Quebec Actual, return fire and check your rear arc!
